'''Shenbit bonecrusher blow''' was a [[Teräs Käsi/Legends|Teräs Käsi]] move, named after the [[shenbit bonecrusher]]. During the [[Palawa Band]] tournament in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]], Teräs Käsi practitioner [[Dux Pike]] was [[Death/Legends|killed]] by [[Phow Ji]] with a shenbit bonecrusher blow.<ref name="Hnn Jedi Defeated for Teräs Käsi">{{HoloNetNewsWeb|55|sports/1359_1.html|Jedi Defeated for Teräs Käsi Title}}</ref>

